---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { getEntry } from 'astro:content';

const entry = await getEntry('pages', 'motel-marketing-strategies-for-independent-operators-increase-direct-bookings-occupancy');
---

<BaseLayout title={entry.data.title}>
  <!-- 1. Executive Hero -->
  <section class="bg-[#F9F9F8] border-b border-stone-200 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#4A554E] mb-4">Marketing Strategy</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight text-balance mb-6">
            {entry.data.title}
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-stone-500 leading-relaxed text-balance">
            Most marketing agencies sell "visibility." They talk about TikTok followers and Instagram likes.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-stone-900">At Motel Coach, we talk about RevPAR and Asset Value.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">
            If you are an <strong class="text-stone-900">Owner</strong>, your website is a capital improvement. Just like a $100k paint job, a high-performance website increases the "Curb Appeal" of your business and significantly raises the valuation of your Management Rights.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">
            If you are a <strong class="text-stone-900">Manager</strong>, you are time-poor. You don't need a "Social Media Manager" to give you more work; you need a system that works while you sleep.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm sticky top-32">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-3">Who this is for</p>
            <blockquote class="text-stone-700 font-medium leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-[#4A554E] pl-4 not-italic">
              "A fresh coat of paint gets them in the driveway. A high-performance website gets them to pay YOU directly."
            </blockquote>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-stone-500">
              Every booking that moves from an OTA to your website puts 15–20% back in your pocket.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. Asymmetrical Content Body -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <aside class="md:col-span-4 order-2 md:order-1">
        <div class="sticky top-32">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-4">On this page</p>
          <nav class="space-y-2">
            <a href="#why-choose" class="block text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-[#4A554E] transition-colors">Why Independent Motels Choose Coaching</a>
            <a href="#big-levers" class="block text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-[#4A554E] transition-colors">The Big Levers</a>
            <a href="#ota-tax" class="block text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-[#4A554E] transition-colors">Stop Paying the OTA Tax</a>
          </nav>
          <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-[#4A554E] hover:text-[#3d4640] transition-colors">
            Speak with an advisor
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 order-1 md:order-2 space-y-16">
        <div id="why-choose">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight text-balance mb-8">Why Independent Motels Choose Coaching Over "Agencies"</h2>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="border border-stone-200 p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#F9F9F8]">
              <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#4A554E] text-white text-xs font-semibold mb-4">01</span>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-2">Generic Marketing Agency</p>
              <ul class="text-stone-500 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-1">
                <li>Focus: "Likes" and Impressions</li>
                <li>Strategy: Post on Social Media</li>
                <li>OTA View: "List on more sites"</li>
                <li>Knowledge: They know "Digital Marketing"</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-stone-200 p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#F9F9F8]">
              <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#4A554E] text-white text-xs font-semibold mb-4">02</span>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#4A554E] mb-2">The Motel Coach Approach</p>
              <ul class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-1 font-medium">
                <li>Direct Bookings & Profit Margin</li>
                <li>Intercept Guests on Google & Maps</li>
                <li>Reduce OTA Dependency & Commissions</li>
                <li>We know Motel Operations</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="big-levers">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight text-balance mb-6">The Big Levers: Where We Focus</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">We don't do everything. We do what moves the needle for a 10-to-40 room independent property.</p>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="border border-stone-200 p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#F9F9F8]">
              <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#4A554E] text-white text-xs font-semibold mb-4">01</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight mb-2">The Digital Front Desk (Conversion)</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">We don't build "brochures." We build high-speed booking engines. If your site doesn't load in under 2 seconds on a patchy regional mobile connection, you are losing money to Booking.com.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-stone-200 p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#F9F9F8]">
              <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#4A554E] text-white text-xs font-semibold mb-4">02</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight mb-2">Google Interception & Local SEO</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">When someone is 10km away and searches "Motel near me," you need to be the #1 choice. We optimize your Google Business Profile to drive phone calls and direct clicks, bypassing the OTA commission.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-stone-200 p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#F9F9F8]">
              <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#4A554E] text-white text-xs font-semibold mb-4">03</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight mb-2">The "Fact Layer" for AI & Search</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Modern travelers (and AI search engines) want data, not fluff. We replace "beautiful rooms" with "King beds, 50Mbps Wi-Fi, and B-Double parking." High-density info wins the booking.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-stone-200 p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#F9F9F8]">
              <span class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#4A554E] text-white text-xs font-semibold mb-4">04</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight mb-2">Revenue & Rate Integrity</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Marketing fails if your pricing is reactive. We help managers implement simple pricing structures that capture peak demand without "discounting" your brand away.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="ota-tax">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight text-balance mb-6">Stop Paying the "OTA Tax"</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-500 leading-relaxed mb-6">Every booking that moves from an OTA to your website puts <strong class="text-stone-900">15-20% back in your pocket.</strong> For a 20-room motel, that is often the difference between a struggling year and a record-breaking one.</p>
          <p class="text-stone-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            <a href="/contact" class="text-[#4A554E] font-medium hover:underline">Book a Free Marketing Audit</a>
            <span class="mx-2">|</span>
            <a href="/motel-consultancy" class="text-[#4A554E] font-medium hover:underline">View Consultancy Options</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
